1
00:00:17,540 --> 00:00:18,220
Hello?

2
00:00:18,780 --> 00:00:21,300
Shen Hao went through a hard time
last night.

3
00:00:21,540 --> 00:00:23,699
He was taken away from your hotel.

4
00:00:23,700 --> 00:00:25,900
Don't you owe me an explanation?

5
00:00:26,100 --> 00:00:27,500
What do I need to explain to you?

6
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:30,199
They're investigating the incident
involving you dumping Minghui's stocks

7
00:00:30,199 --> 00:00:31,620
and manipulating the market.

8
00:00:31,940 --> 00:00:36,739
Shen Gu's lawyer insists on
a thorough investigation of the spiked drink.

9
00:00:36,740 --> 00:00:38,539
The drug belonged to Hao,

10
00:00:38,540 --> 00:00:40,500
and he drank the wine himself.

11
00:00:40,580 --> 00:00:41,579
Let them investigate.

12
00:00:41,580 --> 00:00:42,299
You!

13
00:00:42,300 --> 00:00:43,139
Enough.

14
00:00:43,140 --> 00:00:44,299
I'm hanging up.

15
00:00:44,300 --> 00:00:46,419
Mr. Xu agreed to see me.

16
00:00:46,420 --> 00:00:47,660
I need to get going now.

17
00:01:00,860 --> 00:01:01,980
Dad.

18
00:01:03,700 --> 00:01:04,619
Dad.

19
00:01:04,620 --> 00:01:06,179
You finally agreed to see me.

20
00:01:06,180 --> 00:01:08,860
Do you know how worried I was about you?

21
00:01:13,140 --> 00:01:14,340
Zhaohui,

22
00:01:14,900 --> 00:01:17,620
ask yourself honestly.

23
00:01:18,220 --> 00:01:20,820
After you heard about
your brother's death

24
00:01:20,960 --> 00:01:22,860
and saw me faint,

25
00:01:23,140 --> 00:01:25,019
were you busy vying for
the family assets

26
00:01:25,020 --> 00:01:27,500
or taking care of your family?

27
00:01:28,900 --> 00:01:29,940
Dad,

28
00:01:30,140 --> 00:01:32,019
you can't think that of me.

29
00:01:32,020 --> 00:01:34,219
I was trying to help.

30
00:01:34,220 --> 00:01:35,619
On the day you fainted,

31
00:01:35,620 --> 00:01:37,549
Xu Wanxin and Liu Changhe

32
00:01:37,550 --> 00:01:39,820
drove me out of the house.

33
00:01:39,860 --> 00:01:41,380
Enough with the excuses.

34
00:01:41,580 --> 00:01:45,340
I'm not dead yet,

35
00:01:45,700 --> 00:01:47,740
and you were already
working with outsiders

36
00:01:47,900 --> 00:01:51,820
to hand over Minghui.

37
00:01:52,420 --> 00:01:53,339
Dad,

38
00:01:53,340 --> 00:01:56,660
I admit I wanted the Shen family
to take over the company,

39
00:01:56,900 --> 00:01:58,020
but

40
00:01:58,440 --> 00:02:01,420
that was the only choice we had
at the time.

41
00:02:01,580 --> 00:02:04,620
Do you know who you were going against?

42
00:02:05,030 --> 00:02:07,020
Your own niece.

43
00:02:07,740 --> 00:02:10,219
You teamed up with outsiders
against her.

44
00:02:10,220 --> 00:02:11,620
Against her?

45
00:02:12,380 --> 00:02:15,099
Dad, you've always favored Zhaoming

46
00:02:15,100 --> 00:02:16,299
and Xu Wanxin.

47
00:02:16,300 --> 00:02:18,179
I'm your son too.

48
00:02:18,180 --> 00:02:19,020
Why am I

49
00:02:19,180 --> 00:02:21,060
any worse than them?

50
00:02:21,140 --> 00:02:22,339
Answer me.

51
00:02:22,340 --> 00:02:25,340
What's Minghui's spirit?

52
00:02:28,740 --> 00:02:30,060
To benefit the people

53
00:02:30,380 --> 00:02:31,500
and strengthen the nation.

54
00:02:31,540 --> 00:02:32,460
Oh.

55
00:02:32,700 --> 00:02:34,460
You do remember.

56
00:02:35,420 --> 00:02:37,020
All these years,

57
00:02:37,100 --> 00:02:38,940
we've endured losses

58
00:02:39,020 --> 00:02:42,340
and never stopped investing
in technology research.

59
00:02:42,820 --> 00:02:46,100
It's not that Zhaoming and I
don't know how to make money.

60
00:02:46,380 --> 00:02:48,740
It's our duty to do this.

61
00:02:49,620 --> 00:02:51,220
You're ungrateful.

62
00:02:51,700 --> 00:02:53,940
All you care about
is being a businessman.

63
00:02:54,310 --> 00:02:56,220
That's my failure as a father.

64
00:02:57,100 --> 00:02:59,699
From now on, aside from board meetings,

65
00:02:59,700 --> 00:03:02,420
you're not allowed at the company.

66
00:03:02,860 --> 00:03:05,299
Stay in Gang City

67
00:03:05,300 --> 00:03:07,499
and reflect on yourself.

68
00:03:07,500 --> 00:03:09,020
You're not allowed to go anywhere.

69
00:03:10,100 --> 00:03:11,340
Dad.

70
00:03:14,620 --> 00:03:16,020
Alright.

71
00:03:19,700 --> 00:03:20,820
Dad.

72
00:03:21,780 --> 00:03:23,100
Take care.

73
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:30,879
=Echoes of Gang City=

74
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:34,440
=Episode 9=
(Memory Fragments from 90 Years Ago)

75
00:03:40,420 --> 00:03:42,020
Look at this.

76
00:03:43,820 --> 00:03:44,899
Look.

77
00:03:44,900 --> 00:03:47,540
The tree hasn't changed at all.

78
00:03:58,180 --> 00:04:02,100
This place holds memorial tablets
for someone important to Grandfather.

79
00:04:02,220 --> 00:04:04,020
On every important holiday,

80
00:04:04,180 --> 00:04:06,580
he would come here to pray,

81
00:04:06,700 --> 00:04:08,100
regardless of the weather.

82
00:04:08,700 --> 00:04:10,340
Later, when he got older,

83
00:04:10,700 --> 00:04:12,380
my dad came in his place.

84
00:04:13,380 --> 00:04:14,500
In the future,

85
00:04:15,700 --> 00:04:17,020
it'll be me.

86
00:04:19,300 --> 00:04:20,980
Grandfather devoted himself
to these prayers.

87
00:04:21,820 --> 00:04:23,820
All he wishes for will surely come true.

88
00:04:32,780 --> 00:04:34,500
Let me show you this.

89
00:04:40,540 --> 00:04:41,819
I want to make a wish here.

90
00:04:41,820 --> 00:04:42,980
It's very effective.

91
00:04:43,140 --> 00:04:44,340
Alright.

92
00:04:44,460 --> 00:04:45,819
Has Qianmo gone inside to pray?

93
00:04:45,820 --> 00:04:46,940
Mm.

94
00:04:57,500 --> 00:04:58,620
Look at this.

95
00:05:03,980 --> 00:05:05,900
Mr. Shen. Miss Lin.

96
00:05:07,740 --> 00:05:08,979
Put a prayer slip on it.

97
00:05:08,980 --> 00:05:10,220
It'll surely work wonders.

98
00:05:10,380 --> 00:05:11,620
Let me see.

99
00:05:12,380 --> 00:05:15,740
May Lin Shuyi and Shen Gu be together

100
00:05:16,180 --> 00:05:17,700
for lifetime after lifetime.

101
00:05:21,980 --> 00:05:23,100
Shuyi.

102
00:05:23,700 --> 00:05:24,820
Careful.

103
00:05:26,100 --> 00:05:28,980
I'm going to hang this the highest.

104
00:05:29,900 --> 00:05:31,300
That's not quite proper.

105
00:05:31,380 --> 00:05:33,420
We should wait until our families
find a matchmaker

106
00:05:33,620 --> 00:05:35,380
and I formally propose to your father.

107
00:05:35,780 --> 00:05:36,779
Just tell me, yes or no.

108
00:05:36,780 --> 00:05:37,740
I...

109
00:05:40,580 --> 00:05:42,300
You're so dense.

110
00:05:50,940 --> 00:05:51,699
Yes.

111
00:05:51,700 --> 00:05:52,820
I'm willing.

112
00:05:53,060 --> 00:05:54,980
I will be the most devoted man

113
00:05:55,180 --> 00:05:57,100
among all the red ribbons on this tree.

114
00:05:57,860 --> 00:05:59,580
You fool. You're beyond forgiveness.

115
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:04,900
You'll have to make it up to me
for the rest of this life, the next life,

116
00:06:05,180 --> 00:06:07,220
and many more to come.

117
00:06:08,620 --> 00:06:11,300
Alright. Lifetimes it is.

118
00:06:18,980 --> 00:06:22,579
Do you think the higher it's hung,

119
00:06:22,580 --> 00:06:24,220
the more the gods will bless it?

120
00:06:25,500 --> 00:06:26,459
I'll go find a ladder.

121
00:06:26,460 --> 00:06:27,779
I know where it is.

122
00:06:27,780 --> 00:06:29,420
I'm good at climbing trees.

123
00:06:31,460 --> 00:06:32,620
We're going to make a wish.

124
00:06:35,580 --> 00:06:39,299
A union of two families. A pact is made.

125
00:06:39,300 --> 00:06:41,099
May your marriage be everlasting

126
00:06:41,100 --> 00:06:42,779
and your match be perfect.

127
00:06:42,780 --> 00:06:44,499
The peach blossoms in full bloom

128
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:46,420
reveal the perfect time for marriage.

129
00:06:46,500 --> 00:06:50,340
May your descendants flourish like
trailing vines, generation after generation.

130
00:06:53,620 --> 00:06:55,540
This jade is my heirloom.

131
00:06:55,900 --> 00:06:58,099
Today, I give it to you

132
00:06:58,100 --> 00:06:59,380
as a token of my sincerity.

133
00:07:02,620 --> 00:07:03,810
Good.

134
00:07:09,060 --> 00:07:10,019
Everyone.

135
00:07:10,020 --> 00:07:12,140
Let's take a group photo.

136
00:07:12,540 --> 00:07:13,019
Sure.

137
00:07:13,020 --> 00:07:13,499
Come.

138
00:07:13,500 --> 00:07:14,300
Please gather around.

139
00:07:18,820 --> 00:07:20,619
Everyone, look here.

140
00:07:20,620 --> 00:07:21,499
(Engaged couple Lin Shuyi, Shen Gu)

141
00:07:21,500 --> 00:07:22,460
Three,

142
00:07:22,500 --> 00:07:23,380
two,

143
00:07:23,500 --> 00:07:24,380
one.

144
00:07:27,950 --> 00:07:29,310
Good.

145
00:07:31,470 --> 00:07:32,419
Everyone,

146
00:07:32,420 --> 00:07:34,659
please proceed upstairs for the banquet.

147
00:07:34,660 --> 00:07:35,339
Please.

148
00:07:35,340 --> 00:07:36,540
This way.

149
00:07:37,260 --> 00:07:38,460
Please head upstairs.

150
00:07:43,140 --> 00:07:44,940
You're mine now.

151
00:07:45,420 --> 00:07:47,020
I'm your fiancé.

152
00:07:47,060 --> 00:07:50,180
You can't shake me off,
even if you go to France.

153
00:07:50,660 --> 00:07:52,580
Why don't you come with me?

154
00:07:54,620 --> 00:07:56,900
You pursue your dreams,

155
00:07:57,060 --> 00:07:59,139
and I'll stay to look after
our parents

156
00:07:59,140 --> 00:08:00,499
and the business.

157
00:08:00,500 --> 00:08:02,420
That way, everyone can be at ease.

158
00:08:02,500 --> 00:08:03,620
Gu,

159
00:08:04,020 --> 00:08:05,620
you always have excuses.

160
00:08:10,300 --> 00:08:13,540
I prepared a whole box of gold-flecked
paper to write you letters.

161
00:08:14,300 --> 00:08:16,460
What if I don't reply?

162
00:08:16,860 --> 00:08:18,340
What will you do?

163
00:08:18,820 --> 00:08:22,740
I'll chase you to the ends of the earth.

164
00:08:23,500 --> 00:08:24,659
Gu,

165
00:08:24,660 --> 00:08:26,140
wait for me to come back.

166
00:08:26,700 --> 00:08:27,820
Miss me.

167
00:08:27,860 --> 00:08:28,980
Mm.

168
00:08:39,620 --> 00:08:41,140
Mr. Xu.

169
00:08:46,420 --> 00:08:48,740
The ritual is ready.

170
00:08:48,860 --> 00:08:50,460
Please come with me.

171
00:08:51,340 --> 00:08:54,259
I'll go inside for the ritual.

172
00:08:54,260 --> 00:08:55,540
Wait here.

173
00:08:55,660 --> 00:08:56,540
- Alright.
- Sure.

174
00:08:57,860 --> 00:08:59,380
Be careful, Grandfather.

175
00:09:05,380 --> 00:09:09,180
(Sir and Miss reunited here.)

176
00:09:10,100 --> 00:09:14,660
(I, Xu Qianmo, return
to redeem my vow.)

177
00:09:14,940 --> 00:09:21,020
(May my son, Xu Zhaoming,
be granted another life to return.)

178
00:09:26,220 --> 00:09:27,419
Everything follows

179
00:09:27,420 --> 00:09:28,940
the law of cause and effect.

180
00:09:29,020 --> 00:09:30,940
Your wish has been fulfilled.

181
00:09:31,020 --> 00:09:34,140
You can have this back.

182
00:10:05,300 --> 00:10:07,740
Mr. Shen, a letter from Miss Xu!

183
00:10:15,020 --> 00:10:16,580
(My Mr. Shen,)

184
00:10:16,590 --> 00:10:18,819
(I have settled down in France.)

185
00:10:18,820 --> 00:10:20,860
(I miss you so much.)

186
00:10:21,900 --> 00:10:23,420
(Love)

187
00:10:23,500 --> 00:10:25,140
(isn't enough to describe how I feel.)

188
00:10:25,620 --> 00:10:27,940
(I only know I love you more
with each passing day.)

189
00:10:28,540 --> 00:10:31,220
(If only I could become a breeze
in the dream,)

190
00:10:31,300 --> 00:10:32,820
(cross the seas,)

191
00:10:33,100 --> 00:10:35,420
(and ease the frown on your face.)

192
00:10:37,180 --> 00:10:41,180
(Today, I heard in France
that Shen City has fallen.)

193
00:10:42,020 --> 00:10:43,179
(It's blood everywhere.)

194
00:10:43,180 --> 00:10:44,740
(Wolves and lackeys roam the streets.)

195
00:10:45,220 --> 00:10:47,059
(I worry about)

196
00:10:47,060 --> 00:10:48,620
(our country and our family every day.)

197
00:10:50,220 --> 00:10:52,420
(I think of you and Father's situation.)

198
00:10:52,980 --> 00:10:55,060
(The sorrow in my heart)

199
00:10:55,660 --> 00:10:58,380
(cannot be described in words.)

200
00:11:00,700 --> 00:11:06,250
♪It feels like we have carried so much♪

201
00:11:07,620 --> 00:11:13,050
♪So many questions time itself
could not make clear♪

202
00:11:14,210 --> 00:11:19,580
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

203
00:11:20,650 --> 00:11:26,790
♪Every dream I had became something
I want with you near♪

204
00:11:30,980 --> 00:11:32,460
(A letter to my wife.)

205
00:11:32,820 --> 00:11:35,540
(My dearest, I hope
this letter finds you well.)

206
00:11:36,660 --> 00:11:38,460
(You have been away for three months.)

207
00:11:38,740 --> 00:11:41,940
(The spring in Shen City has faded.)

208
00:11:42,420 --> 00:11:44,780
(The peach blossoms bloom
in the mountain temple)

209
00:11:46,420 --> 00:11:47,820
(reminds me of the years)

210
00:11:48,060 --> 00:11:50,180
(when we walked side by side.)

211
00:11:51,220 --> 00:11:52,820
(But now I think of it,)

212
00:11:53,060 --> 00:11:54,620
(my heart feels empty.)

213
00:11:54,700 --> 00:11:56,260
(I miss you deeply.)

214
00:11:57,940 --> 00:11:59,580
(If not for the times we live in,)

215
00:12:00,220 --> 00:12:02,139
(I could not leave our parents
and hometown,)

216
00:12:02,140 --> 00:12:03,980
(nor my business.)

217
00:12:04,620 --> 00:12:06,060
(The nation is in turmoil.)

218
00:12:06,180 --> 00:12:09,380
(It demands we stand and resist.)

219
00:12:11,260 --> 00:12:13,479
(My wife stays abroad
and broaden your horizons,)

220
00:12:13,479 --> 00:12:15,500
(learning how to strengthen
and protect our country.)

221
00:12:16,020 --> 00:12:17,740
(Everything at home is well.)

222
00:12:18,040 --> 00:12:19,719
(Father also asked me to tell you)

223
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:22,400
(to take his will as your own
and not to return for now.)

224
00:12:23,560 --> 00:12:24,920
(When all is settled,)

225
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:27,360
(we will meet again.)

226
00:12:41,040 --> 00:12:42,169
Hang in there, Mr. Lin.

227
00:12:42,170 --> 00:12:44,920
Put that away.

228
00:12:47,560 --> 00:12:49,400
I have something to say.

229
00:12:49,680 --> 00:12:51,600
Please go on.

230
00:12:51,960 --> 00:12:54,480
My lifelong ambition

231
00:12:55,800 --> 00:12:58,240
is to benefit the people

232
00:13:00,280 --> 00:13:03,400
and strengthen the nation.

233
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:10,200
Shuyi and you

234
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:14,920
must carry on

235
00:13:15,750 --> 00:13:18,280
that will.

236
00:13:21,680 --> 00:13:22,800
We will.

237
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:25,560
Shuyi

238
00:13:26,320 --> 00:13:29,640
is stubborn.

239
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:33,000
You must not let her know

240
00:13:35,280 --> 00:13:38,920
about my situation.

241
00:13:39,920 --> 00:13:41,880
Let her stay in France

242
00:13:42,280 --> 00:13:44,720
in peace.

243
00:13:49,520 --> 00:13:53,000
I will leave the Lin family

244
00:13:56,160 --> 00:13:59,000
to you.

245
00:14:00,080 --> 00:14:02,000
I'm counting on you.

246
00:14:04,574 --> 00:14:07,600
Alright.

247
00:14:23,720 --> 00:14:25,120
Shen Gu.

248
00:14:26,560 --> 00:14:28,400
Keep this in mind.

249
00:14:33,880 --> 00:14:36,240
Never forget our country.

250
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:40,800
Never forget our family.

251
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:45,880
Never forget our spirit.

252
00:14:47,480 --> 00:14:48,760
Never forget

253
00:14:52,680 --> 00:14:54,520
my will.

254
00:14:55,080 --> 00:14:56,400
I won't.

255
00:14:56,880 --> 00:14:58,400
I remember.

256
00:14:59,120 --> 00:15:00,520
I remember, Mr. Lin.

257
00:15:01,720 --> 00:15:03,010
I do.

258
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:24,720
Mr. Lin.

259
00:15:27,520 --> 00:15:28,640
Mr. Lin.

260
00:15:29,120 --> 00:15:29,679
Mr. Lin!

261
00:15:29,680 --> 00:15:30,239
Shanyue!

262
00:15:30,240 --> 00:15:31,199
Mr. Lin!

263
00:15:31,200 --> 00:15:31,999
Shanyue!

264
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:33,079
Mr. Lin!

265
00:15:33,080 --> 00:15:34,520
Shanyue!

266
00:15:45,560 --> 00:15:46,919
Shanyue!

267
00:15:46,920 --> 00:15:48,680
Mr. Lin!

268
00:15:54,240 --> 00:15:55,360
Shen Gu.

269
00:15:56,480 --> 00:15:57,840
I'm sorry for your loss.

270
00:16:03,240 --> 00:16:05,760
They killed my father-in-law.

271
00:16:06,640 --> 00:16:08,760
They intended to install a puppet
in power.

272
00:16:09,840 --> 00:16:12,080
Mr. Lin refused to comply,

273
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:14,040
so they killed him.

274
00:16:14,360 --> 00:16:18,360
Now all seven cargo ships
of the Lin shipping line

275
00:16:19,640 --> 00:16:21,800
have been sunk in the Huangpu River.

276
00:16:29,760 --> 00:16:31,560
We must protect the shipping route

277
00:16:32,680 --> 00:16:34,960
and transport supplies from Gang City.

278
00:16:37,480 --> 00:16:40,240
Only I can do this.

279
00:16:42,080 --> 00:16:44,750
Have you thought it through?

280
00:16:50,720 --> 00:16:52,160
My father-in-law and I

281
00:16:53,440 --> 00:16:55,440
were prepared to sacrifice long ago.

282
00:16:57,280 --> 00:16:59,160
I'll support you fully.

283
00:16:59,720 --> 00:17:01,440
But from now on,

284
00:17:02,080 --> 00:17:04,760
no one can know your true identity.

285
00:17:05,240 --> 00:17:07,360
We have to keep it from everyone,

286
00:17:07,650 --> 00:17:09,120
including Shuyi.

287
00:17:24,760 --> 00:17:26,080
Mr. Shen,

288
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:29,480
a letter from Miss Xu!

289
00:17:36,560 --> 00:17:37,959
(My love.)

290
00:17:37,960 --> 00:17:39,599
(My Mr. Shen.)

291
00:17:39,600 --> 00:17:41,160
(May these words feel like we have met.)

292
00:17:41,560 --> 00:17:43,720
(When you read this,)

293
00:17:44,160 --> 00:17:46,120
(I have decided to return.)

294
00:17:47,040 --> 00:17:49,040
(Everything has me worried.)

295
00:17:50,040 --> 00:17:52,640
(I cannot bear to leave you alone
to face storms.)

296
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:54,919
(I miss our home)

297
00:17:54,920 --> 00:17:56,079
(From your wife, Shuyi)

298
00:17:56,080 --> 00:17:57,240
(and country,)

299
00:17:57,760 --> 00:17:59,280
(I cannot find peace)

300
00:17:59,440 --> 00:18:01,440
(in a foreign land.)

301
00:18:02,420 --> 00:18:04,080
(Wait for me to return.)

302
00:18:04,250 --> 00:18:05,960
(We will marry)

303
00:18:06,800 --> 00:18:08,440
(and protect our home and our country.)

304
00:18:15,200 --> 00:18:22,480
(In Mourning)

305
00:19:07,620 --> 00:19:13,420
♪Tonight the rain falls soft and slow♪

306
00:19:14,700 --> 00:19:20,500
♪Blending with letters left unread
drifting through the air♪

307
00:19:21,220 --> 00:19:26,580
♪You turn and look back at me♪

308
00:19:27,700 --> 00:19:33,220
♪In those same eyes familiar tears
quietly appear♪

309
00:19:34,060 --> 00:19:39,700
♪It feels like we have carried so much♪

310
00:19:40,980 --> 00:19:46,460
♪So many questions time itself
could not make clear♪

311
00:19:47,580 --> 00:19:52,900
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

312
00:19:54,060 --> 00:19:59,860
♪Every dream I had became something
I want with you near♪

313
00:20:00,260 --> 00:20:07,220
♪How many letters have I written
just for you?♪

314
00:20:07,340 --> 00:20:13,020
♪If only you could truly hear
what my heart is trying to say♪

315
00:20:13,700 --> 00:20:20,059
♪From this life on no distance
could keep us apart♪

316
00:20:20,060 --> 00:20:22,939
♪The promise we made♪

317
00:20:22,940 --> 00:20:26,619
♪Will find its way
to be fulfilled one day♪

318
00:20:26,620 --> 00:20:33,219
♪But I want more
than just that fleeting gaze♪

319
00:20:33,220 --> 00:20:39,620
♪Still I have not heard your answer♪

320
00:20:40,020 --> 00:20:46,339
♪Can we still rewrite the ending
we face?♪

321
00:20:46,340 --> 00:20:51,460
♪When regrets begin to turn around you
will hear it all♪

322
00:20:51,940 --> 00:20:54,940
♪Everything that leads me back to you♪
